{"tid":769672,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「英法咩屌你老母」北京研「台灣海峽隧道」建造方案　或單方面以小型項目「熱身」","createTime":"2018-08-06T11:06:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-06T13:37:50.000Z","uid":35430,"like":3,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"7677a5b58e15166a3d7161e0e241c69b0e12fe8c","tid":769672,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T11:06:41.000Z","msg":"中國提出建造連接台灣的「海峽隧道」構想已久，若成事的話，將會是世界上最長、建設難度最大的海底隧道，但一直「只聞樓梯響」。《南華早報》報道，中方工程技術已研發出建造方案，現時有計劃先行建造較小型的海隧工程作「熱身」。不過報道同時引述，學者認為兩岸政治關係緊張，要建成「台灣海峽隧道」，可能與「登月難度」相差不遠。<br />\n<br />\n這個跨越中台海峽的隧道構想，輾轉被提及出近百年。直至2016年初，中國國務院公布「十三五」規劃綱要草案，內容包括解造一條「京臺高速鐵路」。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述消息指出，在去年底，中方才在工程技術上研發出建造方案。報道引述一名不具名政府科學家稱，此項目設計由國家科學委員會支持的中國工程院資助，形容這將是 21 世紀其中一項「最大」和「最具挑戰性」的工程項目。<br />\n根據最新的計劃，這「海底隧道」將會較2016年的構想長數公里，由福建東部平潭島開始「下水」，平潭島是一個2013年開展、對台自由質易的「綜合實驗區」，「海底隧道」再在近台北的新竹市「上水」。按照有關設計，「台灣海峽隧道」完成的話，高鐵列車會以時速 250 公里，在長達135公里的隧道行走，將是全世界最長的列車隧道。<br />\n<br />\n項目在「十三五」規劃初次提出，當時預計可在2030建成。不過暫時來說，這計劃可能只仍是空想。兩岸關係一直緊張，尤其是兩年前民進黨蔡英文勝出台灣總統大選後，無論在外交和軍事方面，中國均向台施壓，尤其是蔡英文政府拒絕承認台灣是「中國的一部份」。兩岸關係相信在短期內不會有變，即是說這條把台灣與中國連起來的「海底鐵路」，亦因而難以成事。不過有科學家指，北京有可能會單方面開展工程，作為擺出「象徵式」的政治姿態。<br />\n<br />\n中國構想中的「台灣海峽隧道」與「英法海底隧道」相似，會由三條管道組成，主要是兩條鐵路管道，中間一條用作安放電纜、通訊電纜和緊急通道的服務隧道，而管道的大小，將比「英法海底隧道」大三份一，容許列車盛載更重貨物和行走得更快。在兩岸海峽中，將要建造一對人工島，以用作泵新鮮空氣進各管道的空氣處理站。<br />\n<br />\n正研平潭島連接福清市<br />\n為「台灣海峽隧道」作準備，中國擬進行較小型、使用差不多技術的項目「熱身」。《南華早報》報道，有研究小組研究由福建平潭島到福清市，建一條逾11公里、造價約 120 億的「海底行車隧道」之可行性，開始作地質磡探、採集石頭樣本、進行電腦模擬，以及分析大型隧道項目的對環境造成影響。該管道會有雙向行車線，每條行車線可讓三部卡車並排行駛，研究結果將於明年提交北京政府。成事的話，這條隧道將超越「東京灣跨海公路」，成為全世界最長的「海底行車隧道」。<br />\n北京交通大學经濟管理學院教授趙堅，專門研究中國重點交通基建經濟表現，他指，中國若在未與台灣達成協議下開展工程，此舉將對台灣的「反中」情緒，火上加油，「這不會將（對台）關係拉近，只會把他們推開得更遠」。"},{"pid":"e374533a5ae8e8338789f2b976049b6241d8a929","tid":769672,"uid":35430,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T11:07:47.000Z","msg":"你唔入水我話你好野呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又黎高鐵侵略2.0"},{"pid":"e23de595fedcd19562a5531f5e7ff1e71186751f","tid":769672,"uid":55924,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T11:09:34.000Z","msg":"地震帶 完"},{"pid":"fab401e14eaa788fc098fe625f6b51473d5307b7","tid":769672,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T11:10:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef26e9f94af3eef12d9bd59e76db00a832239108","tid":769672,"uid":35430,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"e23de595fedcd19562a5531f5e7ff1e71186751f","tid":769672,"uid":55924,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T11:09:34.000Z","msg":"地震帶 完"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T11:11:18.000Z","msg":"多難興邦先唔怕區區地震帶<br />\n13億人多多都夠死"},{"pid":"dd35929ce3294d002cd5aeffbc309b876180f293","tid":769672,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T11:42:07.000Z","msg":"磁能線，預計2030遷都南京添呀"},{"pid":"4e6de7a51b18336e48c3e409e016f7f67d1d8624","tid":769672,"uid":52459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T11:44:17.000Z","msg":"台灣人唔會咁易屈服，雖然有好多共碟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9d13c9a3b8cbdfb3f28530ad3ed74eb52d4298d","tid":769672,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e23de595fedcd19562a5531f5e7ff1e71186751f","tid":769672,"uid":55924,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T11:09:34.000Z","msg":"地震帶 完"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T11:45:27.000Z","msg":"仲夠膽整tunnel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8989308d8f4bde0065062d9e8742a427208a369d","tid":769672,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T11:46:57.000Z","msg":"痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"108b844f39d8abdafa725a1c48c064990ef68d6b","tid":769672,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T11:53:36.000Z","msg":"隧道好似行唔到咁高速<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1643268c910f18d318e0de73f8c2ae2960eb9a7f","tid":769672,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T11:57:06.000Z","msg":"台灣海峽咁深咁大浪<br />\n<br />\n係咪鳩吹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b48b8402101671998100ddbc423a0ee86f814861","tid":769672,"uid":100276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T12:01:47.000Z","msg":"引支那入關，儍仔先起"},{"pid":"13a3ff7449c070db5de91cd7f11c2390dd26e1d4","tid":769672,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T12:05:46.000Z","msg":"一地兩檢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93e040a911e064a95f9e4676ccd4463fbcee6b28","tid":769672,"uid":17672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T12:11:48.000Z","msg":"試吓中日隧道 或者中美隧道啦不如"},{"pid":"c7f1d0bf8a451d0acd07d09046e264a778c7b218","tid":769672,"uid":41245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T12:13:00.000Z","msg":"幾年前先話起橋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗好起咩未呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2fc68280725093257e37b514a4043315ee27cb3","tid":769672,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T12:13:09.000Z","msg":"2030完成統一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d3389d7e3d8861ff143d5e746d97aa8379879f1","tid":769672,"uid":169310,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T12:16:33.000Z","msg":"港豬澳2.0。到時隧道漂移，又話冇問題，不過我依家就住台灣，唔知中共滅先定修隧道起先呢"},{"pid":"263704354186a70aec29fa8b8e1ed579bfd2ce6f","tid":769672,"uid":9694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T12:17:35.000Z","msg":"條隧道方便運兵運資之餘，果對人工島仲可以建設軍事基地，安裝地對空導彈及反艦導彈和跑道方便戰機升降<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32a002eb45a65d0a17c1b95997ad4e859a25ed7d","tid":769672,"uid":34197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T12:19:20.000Z","msg":"單方面建造<br />\n咁條隧道係咪即係去到中間就係掘頭路要折返?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dfa528593a1e7f528570aec53b6f06fd6d68316","tid":769672,"uid":93784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T12:21:47.000Z","msg":"係都連去美國西岸啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4597415c6dad8c9b9692a44252868bff27a129be","tid":769672,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5dfa528593a1e7f528570aec53b6f06fd6d68316","tid":769672,"uid":93784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T12:21:47.000Z","msg":"係都連去美國西岸啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T12:28:02.000Z","msg":"講到人地肯俾你起咁<br />\n以為台灣係香港咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9683daf069d143ced5dd0e6be4460b994e60cd5d","tid":769672,"uid":37661,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T12:31:11.000Z","msg":"真係鳩噏無極限。<br />\n<br />\n臺灣地震死跨海光纖都唔係新聞啦，仲話隧道？<br />\n<br />\n用海綿做呀？"},{"pid":"2b1381664ba3b07f05e771f05d9c99074820a885","tid":769672,"uid":161990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T12:38:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一帶一路咩"},{"pid":"b649409de3b44fa61770223cc683c4e531e22106","tid":769672,"uid":165213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T12:38:27.000Z","msg":"容許列車盛載更重貨物和行走得更快<br />\n<br />\n運坦克車啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f02cbde9485394a50dc3da00a2f58a5f6c80830","tid":769672,"uid":51720,"like":0,"di